be.idamediafoundry.sofa.livecycle.dsc.util

Interface ComponentInfoExtractor<S,O,C,P,F>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractQDoxComponentInfoExtractor, AnnotationDrivenQDoxComponentInfoExtractor, DocletDrivenQDoxComponentInfoExtractor

    public interface ComponentInfoExtractor<S,O,C,P,F>
    Interface defining extraction methods to populate the component model. Only simple attributes and text values should be populated, nested elements should be populated in their own specific methods.
    Author:
    Mike Seghers
